getPropertyValues

java.util.Set<org.semanticweb.owlapi.model.IRI> getPropertyValues(org.semanticweb.owlapi.model.OWLClassExpression subject,
                                                                  org.semanticweb.owlapi.model.OWLPropertyExpression property,
                                                                  boolean positive,
                                                                  org.semanticweb.owlapi.model.IRI... types)
Looks for the "subject (not) 'has property' object"-like axioms and returns possible objects for the specified subject and property.

Parameters:
subject - entry.
property - property.
positive - true/false if positive/negative axiom should be considered, e.g. "subject _/not 'has property' object"
types - optional array of object ancestors. If the types are specified, only the descendants (or equal) of any of the specified type will be returned.
Returns:
set of objects.
